properties.Name: InvoiceLine
properties.Description: A component of the invoice that details specific products, quantities and values invoiced.

Columns.Name: InvoiceId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Invoice.

Columns.Name: InvoiceLineNumber
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Invoice Line Item.

Columns.Name: Quantity
Columns.Description: The quantity of Products to be invoiced by the invoice line item.

Columns.Name: UnitPriceAmount
Columns.Description: The list unit price of the invoiced line item products.

Columns.Name: SalesPriceAmount
Columns.Description: The actual price invoice for the Product(s), which may differ from the list price.

Columns.Name: InvoiceLineItemNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the invoice line item.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: ItemSku
Columns.Description: The Stock Keeping Unit identifier, which is typically used for inventory-related activities.

Columns.Name: TotalProductInvoiceAmount
Columns.Description: The total amount of product invoiced on the invoice line.

Columns.Name: ChargeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Charge.

Columns.Name: InvoiceLineChargeAmount
Columns.Description:
The amount of the charge invoiced on the invoice line.

Note:
One or more adjustments may be invoiced on the same invoice line (see INVOICE LINE ADJUSTMENT).     However, each Charge is invoiced as a single invoice line item.

Columns.Name: InvoiceLineAdjustmentsAmount
Columns.Description:
The amount of adjustment(s) invoiced on the invoice line.

Note:
One or more adjustments may be invoiced on the same invoice line (see INVOICE LINE ADJUSTMENT).     However, each Charge is invoiced as a single invoice line item.

Columns.Name: OrderId
Columns.Description: The unique number that identifies an Order.

Columns.Name: OrderLineNumber
Columns.Description: The number that identifies the Order Line Item.

Columns.Name: InvoiceLineTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Invoice Item Type.
